# Version Drift Contract

Generated artifacts created from onboarding templates must include:

- `generated_from_template_id`
- `generated_from_template_version`
- `generated_at` (ISO8601 UTC)

## Drift Rules

- Missing `generated_from_template_id` or `generated_from_template_version` => stale => update.
- `generated_from_template_version` older than source template `template_version` => stale => update.
- `generated_from_template_id` mismatch for expected artifact type => stale => update.

## Source of Truth

- Template registry: `~/.cursor/templates/onboarding/_index.yml`
